				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "One-liner with a priest that is arguing with his colleague, after the player participated in their group dialog; \"Some of them want to flee to the city, but others say they can't just abandon the temple, especially with their wounded head priest hovering between life and death\"\r\nThis priest considers fleeing."
